| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5387 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8d1af202-b5df-56c9-84f9-2cf542de16b1"
